# Sorok, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Sorok (; , Sorog) is a rural locality (an ulus) in Okinsky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 739 as of 2010. There are 24 streets.
Geography
Sorok is located 41&nbsp;km south of Orlik (the district's administrative centre) by road. Khurga is the nearest rural locality.
